msgstr "Palvelin- vai asiakastunneli?"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:233
#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:651
